name: NFCNDEFStatus
desc: Constants that indicate status for an NDEF tag.

items.name: case notSupported
items.desc: A status indicating that that tag isn't an NDEF-formatted tag.

items.name: case readOnly
items.desc: A status indicating that the tag supports reading NDEF message data only.

items.name: case readWrite
items.desc: A status indicating that the tag supports reading and writing NDEF message data.
